	@printf "⠀⢉⣉⠛⠿⡆⣯⣉⡭⠍⢂⡔⠂⠀⠀⠁⠻⣿⣿⠁⠀⢀⠘⡠⢜⣀⡾⠀⠀⠀⠀⢃⢸⡏⢩⣕⠊⠀⠉⠂⠀⠠⢂⡀⠀⠡⣓⡀⠀⠀⢀⣿⣿⣿⣟⢹⣿⠿⣪⣿⣿⣈⠤⠈⠁⣤⣶⡿⠉⠩⣥⠀⠀⠀⠀⠉⣠⢆⠀⡣⠍⠱⠷⣒⣬⡺⣬⣿⣥⣶⣶⣶⣿⣿⣿⠀⠈⠀⠨⠈⠑⠒⠙⢏⠀⢹⣿⣿⣶⣒⠩⠑⢽⢩⠉⠀⠘⠃\n"
